<p><br />
</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/index.php?title=Scorpion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Availability">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Availability"> Availability </span></h2>
<p>At least one Scorpion variant is available at every <a href="/index.php/Split_Shipyard" title="Split Shipyard">Split Shipyard</a>.
</p>
