</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/index.php?title=Scorpion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Suggested Roles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Suggested_Roles"> Suggested Roles</span></h2>
<p>A pack of these ships make good interceptors, and it is a favorite M4 amongst players with good evasive skill.
</p>
